text: Theodorus Antoon "Theo" Saat (13 May 1928 - 2 June 2015) was a Dutch sprinter. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics in Helsinki, Finland. He was born in Arnhem, Gelderland. Saat died on 2 June 2015 in Noordwijk, South Holland, aged 87. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2015 deaths Category:1952 Summer Olympics Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from Arnhem Category:Dutch sprinters
